description: An ancient tree stump, cut clean as if by a saw, sits to the northeast of the path here.  Something small and furry perchs warily on the stump, barely visible in the dark, watching travelers on the path.

An ancient tree stump, cut clean as if by a saw, sits to the northeast of the path here.  Ravens perch warily on the stump, watching travelers on the path.  Seagulls circle overhead, but do not land on this stretch of path.
title: [Vornavian Coast, Coastal Cliffs]
